About Chromatic

Chromatic is a passion project by two developers, first launched on GitHub in June 2025. The original version looked nothing like the vibrant cyberpunk hub you see today!

Chromatic is your all-in-one neon portal for unblocked games, powerful apps, a stealthy proxy, and full customization—all wrapped in a glowing pink theme.

Stay cyber, stay chromatic.
Created by Ummmyah (Stylist & Graphics) and Justa5thgrader (Developer)
